not only is concern addressed in leaders public statements 
but latin american governments have begun to act and act 
decisively with us experts predicting our nations cocaine use 
levels may have peaked there is genuine concern in latin america 
and elsewhere about where new cocaine markets will open as 
traffickers seek outlets for the andes bumber crop 
