rodeo it is a recognized sporting event in the united states and 
as such is allowed 
were trying to limit the long list of animal exploitation 
going on he said how far do we let this cultural tradition 
go in korea they eat dogs in puerto rico cockfighting is 
legal 
bullfighting originated in crete about 2000 bc and was 
popular for centuries among the wealthy until pope pius v 
concerned about numerous deaths threatened to excommunicate 
practitioners in 1567 the ban did not curb the sports popularity 
in spain however and the prohibition was lifted 
it remains popular in spain portugal and latin america the 
bloodless velcro version has been allowed in three other us 
states kansas oklahoma and texas 
poholik said he plans to deny another permit to the bullfight 
promoters alvarado says promoters will appeal that ruling 
