infidelity keep on loving you take it on the run and 
dont let him go all have strong melodies and plenty of 
harmonies they dont hold up under close listening but sound good 
on the radio and the beach 
also included are the earlier singles time for me to fly 
and roll with the changes and their most recent hits cant 
fight this feeling and that aint love 
